Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.88,0:00:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Anzai, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.26,0:00:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,drink my blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.09,0:00:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you some... every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.59,0:00:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The man who attacked the weather reporter
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,jumped from a nearby apartment complex to his death.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.51,0:00:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,A woman was found nearby, stabbed in the abdomen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.88,0:00:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What crazy ideas are you putting in her head?\NA woman was found nearby, stabbed in the abdomen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.26,0:00:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You make it sound so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.42,0:00:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd you tell him about?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.92,0:00:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Blood tolerance? Healing? Life expectancy?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.26,0:00:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She told a devil to drink her blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.38,0:00:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you put her up to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.09,0:00:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I never forced her to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.71,0:00:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.17,0:00:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you transformed just hearing her say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.55,0:00:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Any other physical changes?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.55,0:00:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you make it up? Is it some religion?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.51,0:00:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This baseless nonsense is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.13,0:00:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not baseless. We even have a proven case.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.63,0:00:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,A proven case of cell regeneration\Nafter blood consumption.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.96,0:00:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If I hadn't happened to show up\Nand give you some blood,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.38,0:00:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you'd still have a hole in your lung,\Nand you'd be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.30,0:01:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Did the near-death thing make you forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.05,0:01:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,About how you were listening to\Nthat girl's sob story and she shot you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.42,0:01:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,A devil killed her mother, so she's convinced\Nall devils are blood-sucking rapists.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.88,0:01:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And now she's a terrorist\Nthat kills devils indiscriminately.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.30,0:01:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she the sniper?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.84,0:01:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she worth crying over?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.67,0:01:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you feel sorry for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.13,0:01:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You're walking around with human blood,\Nblabbing on about your ungrounded fairytales.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.59,0:01:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You have no ID, you're the definition of suspicious,\Nand you want me to trust you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.67,0:01:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.51,0:01:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Promise to hide me out here for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.30,0:01:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I can give you a proper introduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.59,0:01:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and I do have blood,\Nbut I haven't killed anyone, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.59,0:01:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's one other thing I want to make clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.01,0:01:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,"A sap who always lets his emotions\Nget the better of him...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.51,0:01:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,can never protect anyone."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.09,0:01:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a silent night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.76,0:01:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Eclipse was beginnin'
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.92,0:01:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasaneau setsuna o
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.88,0:02:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Kitto eien to shinjikomu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.26,0:02:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,In darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.84,0:02:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's darker than black
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.05,0:02:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Meikyuu no sora
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.46,0:02:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari o kou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.92,0:02:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If bite your soul
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.76,0:02:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoudou ga mushibande yuku
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.76,0:02:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I... Can I... Can I... Who am I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.30,0:02:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Risei o kakikesu libido
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.21,0:02:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,(Where is my heart?)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.38,0:02:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Kurayami ni
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.67,0:02:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,(Where is my heart?)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.80,0:02:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ochikitta
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.01,0:02:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,(Where is my heart?)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.17,0:02:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Minikui sugata ni natte
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.76,0:02:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hito no namida kareta nara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.17,0:02:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Kimi wa boku o dou omou no ka?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.13,0:02:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotae o oshiete
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.05,0:03:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Makka na chi ga
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.96,0:03:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,(Bloody bonds)\NMakka na chi ga
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.09,0:03:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Kizuna o nurashiai
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.17,0:03:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yowasa o wakeatte
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.76,0:03:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,(Bloody bonds)\NYowasa o wakeatte
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.88,0:03:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Futari wa ikite yuku no ka?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.34,0:03:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Kizu o nameatte
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.63,0:03:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Sei o teigi shiatte
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.13,0:03:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ai o musabotte
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.55,0:03:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an3}Dogmatic
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.55,0:03:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should have
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.05,0:03:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,asked Sakaki to bring this here instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.80,0:03:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He might not want to talk to me right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.51,0:03:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But why should I cry about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.38,0:03:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If anyone wants to cry, it's Anzai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.42,0:03:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Anzai, I brought your ramen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.55,0:03:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave it right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.17,0:03:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true he healed from drinking blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.88,0:03:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well Sawazaki said...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.92,0:03:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,he would report that Anzai was\Nonly shot in the shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.13,0:03:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite all the blood lost,\Nthe wound was shallow, and it healed quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.09,0:03:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He filed a false report?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.59,0:03:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just go cool my head on the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.42,0:04:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Anzai's red eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.55,0:04:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw them for the first time on the day we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.34,0:04:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,When our eyes met on the train, I was afraid of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.96,0:04:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But his red eyes were always...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.26,0:04:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,so full of pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.46,0:04:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.38,0:04:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They always seemed to be crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.55,0:04:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Anzai has protected me all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.46,0:04:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,From bad people, and bad dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.59,0:04:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But I still haven't done anything for him in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.59,0:04:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That startled me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.17,0:04:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I guess I didn't have to run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.96,0:04:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,"A sap who always lets his emotions\Nget the better of him...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.38,0:04:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,can never protect anyone."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.51,0:04:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He's exactly right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.96,0:04:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be able to protect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.71,0:05:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.17,0:05:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a dream. With Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.46,0:05:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and a devil that looked human.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.59,0:05:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenichi Morisawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.13,0:05:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the devil's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.88,0:05:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Should you be sitting up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.67,0:05:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That weather girl is in the next room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.13,0:05:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,She's alive. Good news, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.80,0:05:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,A devilish human.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.34,0:05:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You, too. Congrats on surviving.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.88,0:05:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you finish me off?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.38,0:05:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You bit me, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.30,0:05:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like a devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.67,0:05:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It was beautiful, like you had become one yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.84,0:05:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! When they question me,\NI'll tell them you're behind it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.05,0:05:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If you insist. It will only result in more deaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.80,0:05:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'll have to tell him you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.84,0:05:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, your little friend who\Ntold you we'd be executing Plan B.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.34,0:05:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare hurt Zero Nine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.71,0:06:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You betrayed us? Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.88,0:06:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Investigation HQ:\N{\an8}Ikebukuro West Gate Park\N{\an5}TV Broadcast Murder Attempt\NThere were 36 transformations in Tokyo\Ndue to the Ikebukuro incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.21,0:06:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,As for human casualties,\Nthe weather reporter is in critical condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.96,0:06:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The suspect jumped off a building to his death.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.13,0:06:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There were two others in Ikebukuro\Nwith minor injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.38,0:06:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,One in an electronics store in Shinjuku\Nwith minor injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.09,0:06:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,One with minor injuries in an IT firm in Itabashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.96,0:06:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What about devil casualties?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.42,0:06:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The devil in the electronics store\Nwas beaten by the customers there
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.84,0:06:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and died at the hospital later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.38,0:06:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,An officer at Ikebukuro West Gate\Nshot and killed a devil woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.34,0:06:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We have multiple reports of a mob attacking devils\Nin the residential area of Nerima.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.30,0:06:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We have similar incidents happening all over the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.80,0:06:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5}Murder is murder, but will they be convicted\Nlike they would have in the past?\NWe have similar incidents happening all over the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.46,0:06:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5}Murder is murder, but will they be convicted\Nlike they would have in the past?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.47,0:06:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of the laws protecting private information,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.30,0:06:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of the laws protecting private information,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If someone sees a devil for the first time and kills them,\NBecause of the laws protecting private information,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.67,0:06:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If someone sees a devil for the first time and kills them,\Nit will be necessary to...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.13,0:06:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think it's fair to charge them with murder.\Nit will be necessary to...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.26,0:06:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think it's fair to charge them with murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.88,0:06:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going to happen to the\Nconfidentiality policies surrounding devils?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.76,0:06:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Since the media blackout is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.13,0:06:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Will we be commenting on devils\Nat the press conference?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.80,0:07:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We will not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.46,0:07:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Or, to be accurate, we can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.63,0:07:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The MPD doesn't have the authority to decide\Nwhen to go public about devils.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.80,0:07:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The devil issue is a national issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.80,0:07:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, all devil personnel\Nwithin Public Security Division 5
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.63,0:07:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,will be relieved of all duties for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.17,0:07:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what do you mean, "relieved of all duties"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.21,0:07:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't want to deal with the mess\Nif word gets out that the police are harboring devils.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.05,0:07:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.05,0:07:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Your princess brought that to you, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.26,0:07:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is good timing. You can carry her\Nto the guest room, Prince Charming.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.17,0:07:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,She got tired and fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.80,0:07:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She's really not a bad kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.30,0:07:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So you better make sure you're there for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.96,0:07:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not even stirring.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.17,0:07:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She must be exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.42,0:08:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,How do I take them out?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.46,0:08:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That scar really is deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.26,0:08:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.51,0:08:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,My last one, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.76,0:08:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna have to call a donor and get some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.59,0:08:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So they hid the fact that Anzai\Ndrank blood to heal his wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.26,0:08:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, drinking blood is illegal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.67,0:08:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking at it that way, it's almost like\NONLO is exempt from the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.67,0:08:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Since they were doing experiments on drinking blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.46,0:08:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But why is it illegal, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.17,0:08:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Figures. 30 years of blood-sucking cases
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.88,0:09:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and not one mention of a devil\Nhealing after drinking blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.55,0:09:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's true, then why isn't it common knowledge?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.59,0:09:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Serial Fatal Blood-sucking Assaults\N{\an4}Suspect: Anzai, Tamaki\N{\an4}Investigation period: 3/5/1971 - 10/9/1973\N{\an5}Sentence: Death
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.13,0:09:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Sawazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.88,0:09:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.59,0:09:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We got a call from someone who saw\Nsomeone get pushed from the apartment complex.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.13,0:09:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It was too dark to make out a face,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.09,0:09:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,but he was definitely pushed\Nover the rail on the stairway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.38,0:09:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's the informant?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.34,0:09:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone who works at the bar behind the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.71,0:09:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryunosuke Katagiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.30,0:09:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a beautiful day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.09,0:09:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's starting to look like spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.26,0:09:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.21,0:09:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's starting to snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.46,0:09:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What was I just dreaming about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.17,0:10:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I usually remember my dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.92,0:10:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you get in touch with the informant?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.09,0:10:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'm on my way to the bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.88,0:10:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll drive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.30,0:10:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,B Squad has more humans than it needs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.17,0:10:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.09,0:10:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5}Miwako Toda
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.51,0:10:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Miwako? It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.42,0:10:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You finally picked up! Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.13,0:10:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.92,0:10:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,"Why"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.13,0:10:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There are pictures and videos of the\NIkebukuro thing last night all over the internet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.63,0:10:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of those pictures are of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.88,0:10:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Pictures of you running away\Nfrom what looks like a vampire.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.71,0:10:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Pictures of vampires attacking people,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.96,0:10:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,pictures of people beating vampires,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.42,0:10:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,pictures of vampires jumping around like ninjas.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.96,0:10:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't possibly be real.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.13,0:10:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to be some kind of epic prank\Nsomeone set up, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.76,0:10:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Miwako, vampires really do exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.17,0:10:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally they look like all the rest of us,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.80,0:10:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,but they lose control of themselves\Nwhen they see blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.26,0:10:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So they spend their lives\Ntrying to avoid the sight of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.92,0:10:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.01,0:11:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about if it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.84,0:11:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.34,0:11:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, you said the guy you liked\Ncould jump really high.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.51,0:11:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He can jump from phone pole to phone pole.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.38,0:11:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But listen, I know I can trust him, so it's ok-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.30,0:11:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Is trust really the issue here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.05,0:11:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You said they lose control when they see blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.34,0:11:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, it doesn't matter\Nhow much you can trust him, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.42,0:11:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, Tsukasa, you only just met him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.88,0:11:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,How much do you even know about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.13,0:11:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.26,0:11:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just so worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.38,0:11:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.42,0:11:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It hasn't been that long since we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.55,0:11:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's so much I don't know about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.71,0:11:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I could never know how hard it is to be a devil...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.42,0:11:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,or what it's like to lose control.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.13,0:11:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.80,0:11:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He means so, so much to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.55,0:12:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, I missed. I'm in shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.09,0:12:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oryo, dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.88,0:12:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There are other employees here. What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.38,0:12:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If he told them what he saw, they'll be trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.84,0:12:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can kill them, then kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.34,0:12:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't... don't you dare hurt them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.80,0:12:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave these people alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.26,0:12:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a beautiful heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.42,0:12:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I almost can't believe you're a blood-sucking animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.05,0:12:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.38,0:12:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! After them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.17,0:12:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What is going on out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.30,0:12:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll stay here. They might still be at risk!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.96,0:12:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks. I'm borrowing your car.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.01,0:13:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Miwako Toda\N{\an5}Sorry about before. I thought about it,\N{\an5}and if you  trust him, then I trust you.\N{\an5}Anyway, stay safe.\N{\an5}Call me anytime!\N{\an5}And I'll keep an eye on the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.59,0:13:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.51,0:13:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that the guy from the New Year's Eve case?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.46,0:13:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that other guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.09,0:13:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sawazaki, this is Anzai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.42,0:13:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A devil is under attack. It's not our jurisdiction,\Nbut it's an emergency; I'm heading out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.38,0:13:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The target is the trans person from\Nthe New Year's Eve case.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.96,0:13:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He's an informant in the Ikebukuro case!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.38,0:13:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is he now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.13,0:13:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He's running across some rooftops\Nsouth of Bar Sakaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.34,0:13:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see him from my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.76,0:13:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I authorize your deployment, Officer Anzai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.71,0:13:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Go protect the target!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.96,0:13:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Five O'Clock Shadow is\Nthe Touo TV cameraman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.26,0:13:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the guy that kept the camera rolling\Nfrom when the devil drank blood at the plaza
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.09,0:13:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,until I knocked him out\Nafter I explicitly told him not to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.09,0:13:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And while he was filming he kept saying,\N"Just kill him already."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.55,0:13:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I will assist in the arrest, Officer Anzai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.46,0:13:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure talk big for someone\Nwho won't give us his real name.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.76,0:13:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,My real name is Johannes Kleemann.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.59,0:14:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Born in Hybrid Birth Plan Term 15,\NWhite Group Number 7.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.80,0:14:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Raised under the supervision of ONLO in Obihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.17,0:14:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You keep going on and on about identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.96,0:14:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So what term, group, and number are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.21,0:14:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we can talk about that later. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.34,0:14:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If you lose it, I'll just punch your lights out again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.67,0:14:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Lock the door and hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.67,0:14:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hybrid Birth Plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.34,0:14:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought ONLO was just\Nan orphanage for devil children.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.96,0:14:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Attention F Squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.42,0:14:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Anzai has deployed with my permission.\NThis is an emergency situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.38,0:14:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Jill, stand by in the bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.92,0:14:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Again? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.09,0:14:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You both should know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.51,0:14:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,All devil personnel have been\Nremoved from duty for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.51,0:14:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But right now the safety of our target comes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.84,0:14:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We just need to make sure the brass doesn't find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.96,0:15:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I should monitor\NAnzai's temperature and heartrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.09,0:15:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.88,0:15:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You've never monitored me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.34,0:15:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.96,0:15:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,All I know is that ONLO asked me\Nto monitor his health.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.05,0:15:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Note: The Japanese word used for the person who is "it"\N{\an7}in a game of tag means "devil."\NIt's like tag, only this time,\Nthe devil is the one running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.76,0:15:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,As a kid, I always thought it was weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.34,0:15:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one "it." Why don't the runners\Never band together to defeat them?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.38,0:15:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, a transformed devil is vicious,\Nbut it shouldn't take long to figure out...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.59,0:15:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,that humans have the devils hopelessly outnumbered.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.17,0:15:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we humans will chase down the devil "its,"\Nand there'll be even less of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.63,0:15:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Outnumbered, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.21,0:15:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting three-to-one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.09,0:15:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't make him bleed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.01,0:15:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Not even a little nosebleed?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.88,0:15:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you know? Murderers don't have\Nhuman blood in their veins.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.34,0:16:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's not a metaphor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.42,0:16:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.92,0:16:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,His blood is actually ketchup.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.42,0:16:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.30,0:16:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,At least come up with something that's actually funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.09,0:16:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I got your mind off it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.92,0:16:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No more signs of you transforming.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.38,0:16:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So I guess you really do only go full-on devil\Nwhen you're lusting after Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.67,0:16:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Even blood from an old man like me turns you on, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.34,0:16:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I almost feel sorry for you devils.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.51,0:16:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You talk too much, Ketchup.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.76,0:16:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You really don't have to listen to a ketchup like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.46,0:16:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,When you need to pull it out, you need to pull it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.05,0:16:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.59,0:16:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A doctor told me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.34,0:16:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,"Sexual lust comes with bloodlust\Nand vice versa. It's physiological."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.88,0:16:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,"So instead of relying on sedatives,\Na more natural outlet would be masturbation."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.55,0:17:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, got any handcuffs?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.17,0:17:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So you just accept the idea that\Nwe have lusts that lead us to murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.76,0:17:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether you accept it or not,\Nbloodlust is going to exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.34,0:17:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The question is how to control it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.30,0:17:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.55,0:17:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.09,0:17:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Anzai! Where's Katagiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.38,0:17:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.59,0:17:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, aren't you Tsukasa's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.09,0:17:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Lee's here, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.80,0:17:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...\NLee's here, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.55,0:17:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Are the people at the bar alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.84,0:17:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This man said he was going to kill them, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.46,0:17:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I left another detective at the bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.55,0:17:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You said he's an informant on the Ikebukuro case.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.71,0:17:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that why that guy was after him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.92,0:17:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Anzai, hide Katagiri at Bar Sakaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.84,0:17:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't answer any questions\Nfrom the investigation team.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.01,0:17:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Katagiri's tip isn't common knowledge at HQ.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.80,0:17:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Only a few people know about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.17,0:17:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a mole?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.21,0:18:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well. Looks just like his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.88,0:18:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That is a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.17,0:18:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,To think I'd see a child of the light\Nand a child of the dark together in one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.55,0:18:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You're hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.84,0:18:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.63,0:18:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oryo! Why are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.67,0:18:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently he's a vital witness in the Ikebukuro case.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.88,0:18:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell did you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.01,0:18:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,On the news, they said that the suspect\Njumped to his death, but he didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.96,0:18:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.71,0:18:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,As he fell, he was saying something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.84,0:18:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he was saying, "Traitor."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.59,0:18:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Did that happen when he was chasing you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.30,0:18:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This is, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.17,0:18:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No. You did that to yourself,\Nto fend off your bloodlust, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.59,0:19:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw the dead boy's blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.76,0:19:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Devils do it all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.51,0:19:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,One of my coworkers at the bar\Nsaid she used to do it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.55,0:19:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,She was wondering what's going to become of us now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.92,0:19:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5}Are they trolling us? Or is it movie footage?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.46,0:19:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Johannes, take care of Oryo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.38,0:19:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go in through the window and come down\Nwhen my eyes are back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.42,0:19:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But Anzai, you have to get your wounds treated.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.96,0:19:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine. Just go to your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.05,0:19:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.38,0:19:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just how he deals with his bloodlust right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.30,0:19:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa, are you angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.01,0:19:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Bloodlust is going to exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.71,0:19:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't change that fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.71,0:19:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.51,0:19:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,if I admit that this craving is natural,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.63,0:19:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,it would be like I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.30,0:19:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I've been a devil...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.84,0:19:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,since the day I met her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.17,0:19:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You've lost a lot of blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.80,0:19:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to get you to a hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.46,0:20:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But that Sawazaki guy said we have to hide him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.13,0:20:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If we leave him like this, he could die.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.21,0:20:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But what hospitals around here treat devils?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.38,0:20:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirase Hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.46,0:20:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Jill, call Sawazaki for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.76,0:20:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Taira, you go back to the bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.21,0:20:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.38,0:20:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.55,0:20:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We're taking Oryo to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.84,0:20:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to go with them. Stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.67,0:20:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not safe out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.21,0:20:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.05,0:20:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Makimura, give me a status report.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.76,0:20:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in, Makimura!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.34,0:20:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing to report.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.59,0:20:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.13,0:20:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We arrested the guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.42,0:20:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'm looking for Katagiri; he's gone missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.92,0:20:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You stay where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.17,0:20:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood. You be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.21,0:20:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Eleven. Zero Four's been arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.51,0:21:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And there was a human working at Cross Bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.51,0:21:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You told me they were all devils.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.21,0:21:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand incompetence.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.34,0:21:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time you slip up, you're sleeping with the fishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.26,0:21:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero Seven!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.67,0:21:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an4}Shirase\N{\an1}Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.80,0:21:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Uno, you remember this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.21,0:21:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean the sniper?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.80,0:21:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Material Witness\N{\an8}Tenjo, Nanako\NYeah, and I'm sure I've seen that name\Nsomewhere before.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.80,0:21:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Oryo! We're almost there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.84,0:21:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,She's escaping! Hey, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.05,0:21:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is that? A devil?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.80,0:21:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the person who shot Anzai.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.05,0:21:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me the keys to your car!\NOr I'll break her neck!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.05,0:22:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Sotto tokete yuku you ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.59,0:22:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Motto ai shiaetara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.67,0:22:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Nani o tsutaerareta no
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.76,0:22:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ai o tsumugenai meguriawase
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.21,0:22:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Dare ka yurushite
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.42,0:22:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Kegareta sugata ga boku de aru koto o
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.17,0:22:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Aa doushite
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.42,0:22:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Fureru yubi ga furueteiru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.01,0:22:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's story of fight together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.21,0:22:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Dakishimetai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.46,0:22:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Kizu tsukezu ni mamoritai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.17,0:22:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Anata dake o
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.42,0:22:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's story of desire forever
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.01,0:23:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Aragai tsuzukeru
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.59,0:23:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wakiagaru shoudou ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.17,0:23:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,"Aa, mata boku wa..."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.67,0:23:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Deep red dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.26,0:23:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sotto futari tokete yuku you ni...
